title: Sam Walton
added: was an American businessman and entrepreneur best known for founding the retailers [[Walmart]] and [[Sam's Club]]. Wal-Mart Stores Inc. grew to be the world's largest corporation by revenue as well as the biggest private employer in the world.<ref name="rediff">{{cite web | title = Sam Walton Biography | url = https://www.7infi.com/sam-walton-biography-age-weight-height-friend-like-affairs-favourite-birthdate-other/ | work = 7infi.com|access-date=August 10, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810171106/https://www.7infi.com/sam-walton-biography-age-weight-height-friend-like-affairs-favourite-birthdate-other/|archive-date=August 10, 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref> For a period of time, Walton was the richest man in America.
